data.text: @imatastelesshoe OH NOvid i hope ur ok🤍🤍
@imatastelesshoe Hopefully u have someone who can take care of u or drive you to the hospital if u need. Stay positive and hope u get better soon 🤗.
@femmephibian But I don’t have any breathing problems so don’t worry 🥰

@imatastelesshoe Get an ox monitor at CVS. If your breathing is 93 to 89 on it then go to the hospital. Drink lots of fluids and eat what you can keep down. Gatorade for electrolytes. And sleep and lay on your stomach at all times. That's called plaining and it's crucial for airflow. Vitamin c
